Make the pertinent changes in ../OSG/viewer_config/viewer_conf.xsd 

In order to convert a XSD in a Python API we use

generateDS python module

To install it:

pip install generateDS

(need root privileges)

Once installed: 

cd /path/to/PattyDataRepo/python
generateDS.py -f --silence -o viewer_conf_api.py ../OSG/viewer_config/viewer_conf.xsd 